---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Our Studios"
	description="Our two studios, a large Class & Movement Studio and a quieter Early Rehab Studio, are where the real rehab and training happens."
>
	<PageHero
		title="Studios"
		highlight="Our"
		subtitle="Two dedicated spaces for rehab, movement, classes and training, the majority of your recovery happens here."
		breadcrumb="Our Studios"
	/>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Studio 1"
		heading="Class &amp; Movement"
		highlight="Studio"
		image="/our-studios/body-1.jpg"
		imageAlt="Class & Movement Studio, open training space"
	>
		<p>Our large open studio hosts end-stage rehab, speed and agility training, classes, movement sessions, lectures and workshops. Judo mats and exercise matting cover the floor, with equipment positioned around the perimeter.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Bungees fixed to pillars and LifeLine USA train station</li>
			<li>CrossCore 180 Rotational Bodyweight Training kit</li>
			<li>Jungle Gym Suspension training and dips bars</li>
			<li>Heavy boxing and Thai boxing bags</li>
			<li>Olympic bar and plates, Iron Mind sand bags</li>
			<li>Extensive kettlebell range (Competition Steel and Cast Iron)</li>
			<li>Medicine balls, heavy ropes, mobility and myofascial release tools</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Access is available to clients and those who have completed induction, with instruction available from our strength &amp; conditioning coaches.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Studio 2"
		heading="Early Rehab"
		highlight="Studio"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/our-studios/body-2.jpg"
		imageAlt="Early Rehab Studio, balls and quiet training space"
	>
		<p>Our smaller first-floor studio is primarily for early rehab drills treating sports injuries, back pain and neck pain. It's quieter, music-free, and perfect for movement coaching, mobility and flexibility practice.</p>
		<p>It's connected to four treatment rooms and includes a medical room for injections, ultrasound assessments, and visiting practitioners.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
